column16: Placido Polanco pops out to second baseman Adam Kennedy.
Shane Victorino homers (2) on a fly ball to right field.    Carlos Ruiz scores.
Ross Gload pops out to third baseman Alberto Gonzalez.
Juan Castro grounds out softly, third baseman Alberto Gonzalez to first baseman Adam Dunn.
David Wright doubles (1) on a fly ball to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
Alex Cora grounds out, shortstop Ian Desmond to first baseman Adam Dunn.
Chase Utley flies out to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
Placido Polanco hits a grand slam (1) to left center field.   Raul Ibanez scores.    Carlos Ruiz scores.    Jimmy Rollins scores.
